Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.40,0:00:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}可回溯至将近五亿年前
