Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.20,0:00:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}它看尽帝国崛起，衰微
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}王朝兴盛更迭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.44,0:01:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}而且可能历经了 一百五十多万次的日出日落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.28,0:01:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}刺果松是世界上最长寿的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.16,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}竹子则是生长速度最快的植物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.76,0:01:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}短短九十天 就能长到三十公尺高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.68,0:01:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}植物和动物一样 无时无刻不在抢夺食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}努力繁衍后代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.56,0:01:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}对抗掠食动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.92,0:02:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}有的会欺瞒拐骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.60,0:02:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}有的甚至会猎食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.32,0:02:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}《植物》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.60,0:02:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}我们对植物的惊人行为 往往视而不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.56,0:02:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}因为对我们来说，它发生得太慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.36,0:02:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但是若把时间压缩，换个角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.00,0:02:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}由植物的观点出发 它们的世界顿时变得鲜活生动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.32,0:02:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}把半年内在这片林地发生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.36,0:02:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}浓缩至不到一分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.76,0:03:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}和动物一样 植物也需要食物和水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.48,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}植物需要阳光才能生长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}所以它们为了得到充足的阳光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.40,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}会各出奇招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.32,0:04:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}森林似乎是 最适合植物生长的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但是对刚刚萌芽的新生植物来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.72,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}森林的地面是最难讨生活的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.96,0:04:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}上方的树冠层 浓密到只能透出一丝丝阳光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}这棵树苗得不到足够的阳光 只好黯然退出人生舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.72,0:05:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但是地面上的植物 也可以主动出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.96,0:05:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}既然这里照不到光 就到有光的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但它们还是有一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}有光的地方离地面有五十公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}它们只好往上爬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.76,0:05:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}若能把其他植物当踏脚石 往上爬就轻松多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.16,0:05:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但除非能紧紧攀住 否则爬不了多高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}这棵长春藤的黏性吸盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.12,0:06:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}像寻找着力点的指尖一样 紧紧抓住树皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.28,0:06:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}有些植物不会紧黏在树干上 而是伸出利爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.36,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}猫爪藤用卷须勾住微小裂缝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}把自己往上撑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}每向上爬一公尺 阳光就变得更强一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}进一步刺激它生长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.76,0:06:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}这株西番莲的卷须 看似漫无目的地在半空中乱挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.64,0:06:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}其实它在找一个着力点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.84,0:07:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}卷须盘绕起来 把植物拉向它的支撑物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.72,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}短短几天光景 这些攀缘植物就到了树冠层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.84,0:07:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}它们来到明亮的阳光下 肆意地绽放花朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.36,0:07:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}别的植物在拥挤的森林里 以截然不同的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}得到它们所需的光线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}这些是气生植物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}它们生长在 高耸树木的上层树枝上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}终其一生都沐浴在阳光中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.76,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但是在离地五十公尺的地方生长 还是有缺点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.68,0:08:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}大多数的植物利用根部 吸收土壤中的水分和养分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}在树梢扎根的气生植物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}没办法这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但它们也有解决之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}它们光裸的根部吸水力极强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}和吸墨纸不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.40,0:08:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}绝不放过一滴雨水或一丝雾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.56,0:08:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}它们收集养分也自有一套方法
