Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.68,0:08:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}落叶腐烂之后 成为它们专属的堆肥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}以这种惊人方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.56,0:09:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}生存的气生植物有两万种 包括兰花，凤梨和羊齿植物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.52,0:09:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}植物要茂盛生长 光是有养分还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.44,0:09:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}养分还得均衡才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.44,0:09:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}这片沼泽的土壤缺氮 所以土质很差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.92,0:09:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但是这种奇特的植物 有一种别出心裁的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.24,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}它们的叶片上长满了触须
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}触须顶端有一颗看似朝露的液滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.84,0:10:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}所以小毛毡苔又叫做日露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.84,0:10:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}它们气味香甜，引来了许多昆虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.04,0:10:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}但它们也黏得不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.76,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\fscx110\fscy105\b0}沼泽的蚊虫孵化时
